                            <div class="description">
                                <p>The Ghanaian fashion industry has evolved significantly in recent years. Despite
                                    great strides attained, habitual delayed pickups, mixup of client orders and fabric,
                                    coupled with the absence of an organised and secure operational data management on
                                    the part of the fashion designer, have been recurrent themes plaguing this industry.
                                    Surprisingly, in this digital transformation age, there is no market leader
                                    providing productivity tools for our fashion designers. We therefore decided to
                                    step-in and build a service app called Maverick Tailor.
                                    <br>
                                    <br>
                                <p style="color: black;">Maverick Tailor is a tailor-aide Mobile App, designed to enable
                                    fashion designers be
                                    more efficient and productive at work. We strongly believe in simplifying work
                                    processes for every fashion designer. After all, an efficient tailor makes a happy
                                    client!</p>

                                <h5 class="mt-4">The app has the following major functionalities:</h5>
                                <p class="mb-2">1. Record-keeping in a safe and secure data base - capture and save
                                    photo of fabric, client
                                    contact info, measurements,
                                    order details, etc.</p>

                                <p class="mb-2">2. Process invoices and receipts</p>

                                <p class="mb-2">3. Track income and expenses</p>

                                <p class="mb-2">4. Schedule reminders for due dates</p>

                                <p class="mb-2">5. Plan and view tasks in calendar view
                                    Visualization of financial data in charts</p>

                                <p class="mb-2">6. Enhanced correspondence with clients Easy search through data -
                                    client info,
                                    measurements, etc</p>

                                <p class="mb-2">Allows for multiple managers of data
                                    Track status of orders - use of color schemes</p>

                                <p class="mb-2"> Enables sketching of designs
                                </p>
                            </div>
