                                    payments and track deliveries online. Secondly, this E-store platform is built on an
                                    easyto-use Content Management System (CMS) to allow management of food business to
                                    effectively manage and track business business operations.</p>
                                <h5 class="mt-4">Features of The Chopboard</h5>
                                <p class="mb-2">1. A graphically-pleasing store front that readily presents relevant
                                    offers, promotions and products</p>

                                <p class="mb-2">2. A create account/log in feature offering a personalized shopping
                                    experience for each customer. </p>

                                <p class="mb-2">3. The E-Store allows store management/vendors to create as many
                                    attributes for food products as need - food category, meal type, cake flavor, etc
                                </p>

                                <p class="mb-2">4. The E-store allows for comparison of products side-by-side to
                                    eliminate
                                    "guesswork" of customers and facilitating their search; hence, cutting down on the
                                    time spent to purchase items, at the same time, increasing the odds of adding a
                                    selected product to the cart.

                                <p class="mb-2">5. Inventory management, which allows vendors/store management to track
                                    which
                                    products/items/services are the most patronized. This will help guide
                                    decision-making processes for business operations.
                                </p>
