                                <p>Partnering with AlloyBlue Ltd, we served as KNUST’s digital traffic consultant, and
                                    executed a detailed review of the often-overlooked problem of transportation woes
                                    for students in particular, and offered solutions to make campus life easier to
                                    navigate.</p>

                                <p class="mt-4">
                                    Having first conducted a needs survey, we collated their concerns and sought to
                                    address these. To make the shuttle system more efficient, an app has been created to
                                    enable students track the real-time location of shuttles within their reach. This
                                    way, they can more accurately predict which bus stop to approach, in order to catch
                                    a ride soon enough. Second, students can request for help to find their way around
                                    campus, and receive directions to their destinations based on the fastest shuttle
                                    route available to them.The app also lets drivers know specific areas where demand
                                    for service is high, so service can be provided promptly. This helps to eliminate
                                    idle trips made round campus, in search of passengers. The result? A cut down on
                                    fuel expenses.
